Summary: I saw a bright green light fly over my apartment building.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was laying in my chair watching TV in the living room around 1:25am. Something told me to look out the window of my deck door which I had open. Just as I did, I saw a bright green light fly over my apartment building. It was a round shape and the color of it was the same as a green light on a traffic light. It made no sound but was flying very,very fast! It also seemed to be descending. I have never seen anything like it bjpefore, and after it passed I just laid there for awhile not knowing what to think. I forgot to mention that I lost sight of it when it flew over another apartment building across the street.
